          GOTO     OUTDET99
.
          INC       OUTCLIIO/INC
          INC      OUTPREIO/INC
          INC       OUTBOAIO/INC
          INC       OUTMA1IO/INC
          INC       IBAOVRIO/INC
          INC       OUTBB1IO/INC
